title: 'Easy to cut
body: '5.0 out of 5 stars''Quality is good as per the description I have received little bigger than A4 size. I have used them behind multiple acrylic coasters as shared in the pictures.Adhesive quality is good too.'

title: 'adhesive quality is very unsatisfactory'
body: 'while removing the adhesive side cork is coming off. Also the edges are cut unevenly. Overall poor quality'

title: 'The product is very good'
body: 'First by mistake I got a wrong itembut seller soon exchanged for right one.Happy with the quality and delivery.'
